{"article_id":"TtaIvVNPOhXEuLP0","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The birthplace of the free speech movement has become its graveyard .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Hundreds of liberals rioted at the University of California Berkeley Wednesday night","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"-- burning stores ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"throwing Molotov cocktails","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and clashing with police .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Click here for a free subscription to Todd ' s newsletter :","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"a must-read for Conservatives !","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"The rampaging mob forced the university to shut down an event","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"featuring gay conservative firebrand and Breitbart editor Milo Yiannopoulos .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"\" I ' m outraged","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that Milo has been given a platform at UC Berkeley ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and there should be no place for him here , \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"visiting assistant art professor Samara Haplerin told the Daily Californian .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" He should be scared","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that people aren ' t going to stand for this . \"","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Ironically , Milo had planned to deliver remarks","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"defending free speech .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"\" One thing","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"we do know for sure :","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"the Left is absolutely terrified of free speech","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and will do literally anything","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"to shut it down , \"","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"he wrote on Facebook .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Learn how Conservatives can fight back","depth":3},{"id":24,"text":"and reclaim our public universities !","depth":3},{"id":25,"text":"The British conservative journalist called the violence a \" horrible spectacle and very humiliating for American higher education . \"","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"The crowd hurled fireworks at police officers","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and smashed windows at the Martin Luther King , Jr. Student Union .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"They also damaged buildings in downtown Berkeley","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"- including a Starbucks and a number of banks .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"The bloodthirsty mob targeted several supporters of President Trump .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"One young lady","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"wearing a \" Make America Great Again \" hat","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"was attacked during a television interview .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"An unknown man sprayed some sort of liquid in her face .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"The Daily Californian reports","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"another Trump supporter was grabbed by a crowd of agitators","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and thrown to the ground .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"He escaped ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"but they grabbed his red hat","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and set it on fire .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"And police had to rescue another man","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"who was bloodied and beaten .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"The university released a statement","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"blaming the violence on outsiders","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"they allege","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"came to the campus","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"to cause mayhem .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"They also affirmed Milo ' s right","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"to speak on the liberal campus .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" Chancellor Nicholas Dirks made it clear","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"while Yiannopoulos ' views , tactics and rhetoric are profoundly contrary to those of the campus ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"UC Berkeley is bound by the Constitution , the law and the university ' s values and Principles of Community ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"which include the enabling of free expression across the full spectrum of opinion and perspective . \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Those are very nice words","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"- but they are meaningless -","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"unless they are enforced .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"According to the university ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"not a single person was arrested .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Not a single arrest , folks .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Did someone order the police officers to stand down ?","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"If so ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"who gave that order - and why ?","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"So here 's what needs to happen :","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"President Trump should immediately issue an executive order","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"blocking Berkeley students from receiving any federal funding .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"And the same goes for any other public universities","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that want to silence conservative voices .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Universities must guarantee free speech for all students -","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"conservative and liberal .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"It ' s time for the federal government to eradicate this un-American infestation in higher education .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"\" No one ' s safety is at risk from different opinions , \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Milo told \" Tucker Carlson Tonight. \"","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"\" No one ' s physical safety is endangered by political ideas from a speaker on campus ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"but universities have sort of allowed this stuff to happen ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"and even in some cases encouraged it . \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Ironically , it was liberals","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"who silenced a gay immigrant","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and vandalized a building","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"named after a Civil Rights legend .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Who knew","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"there were so many homophobic , racist xenophobes at Berkeley ?","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":167,"left":106,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":90,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":88,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":0,"right":87,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":87,"left":1,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":2,"right":85,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":85,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":97,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":91,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":94,"right":95,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":93,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":92,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":98,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":19,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":107,"right":165,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":23,"right":